name: A Place For Us (To Bleed)
description:
This abstract digital collage is the second machine collab in this series of AI collaborations, where I use generative images based on my own words as source material for my collage work. I really put my heart into the machine with this one. Below is a poem I wrote on the spot before minting, inspired by the collage & various life circumstances.

We wandered for days
in an alien place
unbeknownst to you or I.
Our calloused hearts
churned in glee,
at long last, 
finally.. 
a place for us 
to bleed.
